      <program language="python">
        <input>
cancer_test.info()
        </input>
      </program>
      <pre>
&lt;class 'pandas.core.frame.DataFrame'&gt;
Index: 143 entries, 116 to 15
Data columns (total 12 columns):
 #   Column             Non-Null Count  Dtype  
---  ------             --------------  -----  
